commit.message:
acinclude.m4 (lt_cv_deplibs_check_method): Use pass_all on sh*.

	* acinclude.m4 (lt_cv_deplibs_check_method): Use pass_all on sh*.
	* aclocal.m4, configure: Rebuilt.

From-SVN: r81981

files.patch:
@@ -1,3 +1,8 @@
+2004-05-18  Kaz Kojima  <kkojima@gcc.gnu.org>
+
+	* acinclude.m4 (lt_cv_deplibs_check_method): Use pass_all on sh*.
+	* aclocal.m4, configure: Rebuilt.
+
